text: Josephine Green (born 25 April 1993) is a Welsh footballer who plays as a midfielder and has appeared for the Wales women's national team. ==Career== Green has been capped for the Wales national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Welsh women's footballers Category:Wales women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Manchester City W.F.C. players
